data.description: Fully renovated 4 Bed/2 Bath POOL home in the heart of Oakland Park.  Several updates have been done throughout the house including impact windows/doors, all new interior and a freshly painted exterior, a pool heater, a security system, and plumbing updates. The corner lot offers expansive outdoor living with a spacious front and backyard. The fully fenced backyard includes a water-tight shed, perfect for storage or an additional workshop space. Ideally located just minutes from Lauderdale by the sea, this property is a quick drive from stunning beaches, the Hard Rock Stadium and Casino, exotic restaurants, and world-class shops.
